{{Infobox company | name = Agronic Oy | logo =Agronic R.gif | logo_size = | trading_name = Agronic | industry = [[Heavy equipment]] | founded = 1993, [[Haapavesi]] [[Finland]] | founder = Erkki Kivelä, Urpo Kuronen | products = [[Agricultural machinery]] | revenue = EUR 8,8 million (2016) | num_employees_year = 48 (2016) | website = [http://agronic.fi/en/ agronic.fi/en] }}
'''Agronic''' Oy ('''Agronic''' Ltd.) is a Finnish manufacturer of agricultural equipment. The company is located in [[Haapavesi]], [[Finland]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.is.fi/yritys/agronic-oy/haapavesi/2479928-3/|title=Economical report|last=Taloussanomat|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> Agronic Oy has a daughter company Prodevice Oy.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.prodevice.fi/yritys|title=ProDevice|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref>
Agronic Oy was established by [[Urpo Kurone]]n and [[Erkki Kivelä]] in 1993.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.yrittajat.fi/suomen-yrittajat/palkittuja-yrittajia/valtakunnalliset-palkitut/agronic-oy-322345|title=Yrittäjät|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> The main products are [[Baler#Round baler|round balers]], [[bale wrapper]]s, [[slurry pit|slurry]] tanks and umbilical slurry systems. Around 50% of products are exported to more than 20 countries all over the world. The company co-operates with Japanese company Takakita.
In 2011, Agronic was awarded the National Entrepreneur Prize.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://yle.fi/uutiset/3-5441387|title=Halpa-Halli palkittiin yrittäjäpalkinnolla|last=YLE|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> In 2013, the company became the biggest tax payer in [[Haapavesi]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://yle.fi/uutiset/3-7593895|title=Pyhäsalmen kaivos jälleen yhteisöverojen kärjessä|last=YLE|first=|date=|work=|access-date=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=}}</ref>
